// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1180 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8d249877-12a5-57e5-9ff8-66508e1581a8

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14* OR ImageFileName = *debian:8*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
